2. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with controlling multi-robot systems, which falls under the purview of systems and control. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses algorithms to compute, project and sample from fiber bundles, which is a core area of AI research. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper deals with multi-robot systems, which is a core area of multi-agent systems research. 
5. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper uses fiber bundle diagrams to visualize local minima, which is a geometric approach to the problem.
